        {
            "title": "委內瑞拉將設立石油收入基金並修訂能源法",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 委內瑞拉代總統德爾西·羅德裡格斯提出一項對該國碳氫化合物法的改革方案，並宣布設立兩個基金，石油銷售所得的美元資金將劃入其中。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">羅德裡格斯周四在加拉加斯向議員表示，這些由國家管理的基金將分別用於社會保障和經濟發展。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些基金將「使投資資金得以進入此前從未有過投資、也沒有基礎設施的新區域，」她表示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">兩周前，美國軍隊在對加拉加斯的一次突襲中抓捕了總統尼古拉斯·馬杜羅。唐納德·川普政府表示，計畫無限期控制委內瑞拉未來的石油銷售，並將所得存入美國賬戶。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a89309db-8f13-3e58-bb96-c30dd05ebc3c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：美國稱將無限期掌控委內瑞拉石油出口 能源部長駁斥「偷油」的說法</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">政府尚未公佈碳氫化合物法修改的具體細節，但相關調整很可能會將馬杜羅此前為振興經濟而悄然推出的市場友好型政策正式化。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Venezuela to Set up Funds for Oil Revenues and Amend Energy Law</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A7%94%E5%85%A7%E7%91%9E%E6%8B%89%E5%B0%87%E8%A8%AD%E7%AB%8B%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A5%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E4%B8%A6%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E6%B3%95-230006910.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-16 07:35:50",
